# C#的自定义控件样式

### 以WPF的RadioButton为例子

### 实现的效果

<img src="data:image/png;base64," ></img>

### 代码实现如下：

```XAML
<StackPanel HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Center" Orientation="Vertical">
            <StackPanel.Resources>
                <Style TargetType="RadioButton">
                    <Setter Property="Background" Value="Transparent"/>
                    <Setter Property="Margin" Value="0,5,0,5"/>
                    <Setter Property="Template">

                        <Setter.Value>
                            <!--控制模板-->
                            <ControlTemplate TargetType="RadioButton">
                                <Border Name="border" Width="250" Background="Transparent"
                                        Padding="15,8,8,8">
                                    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="7,0,0,0">
                                        <!--画图-->
                                        <Grid RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5">
                                            <!--旋转45°-->
                                            <Grid.RenderTransform>
                                                <RotateTransform Angle="45"/>
                                            </Grid.RenderTransform>
                                            <!--发光效果-->
                                            <Grid.Effect>
                                                <DropShadowEffect Color="White" BlurRadius="5" ShadowDepth="0"/>
                                            </Grid.Effect>
                                            <!--没有选中的状态-->
                                            <!--方形-->
                                            <Rectangle Name="uncheak" Width="4" Height="4"
                                                       HorizontalAlignment="Center"
                                                       Fill="White"
                                                       StrokeThickness="1"
                                                       VerticalAlignment="Center"/>

                                            <!--选中后的效果-->
                                            <Grid Name="cheak" Visibility="Hidden">
                                                <Rectangle Width="16" Height="16"
                                                       HorizontalAlignment="Center"
                                                       Fill="Transparent"
                                                       StrokeThickness="2"
                                                       Stroke="White"
                                                       VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                                                <Path HorizontalAlignment="Center"
                                                      VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                      Fill="White"
                                                      Data="M0,0 10,0 10,10"/>
                                            </Grid>
                                        </Grid>

                                        <ContentPresenter Name="text" Margin="8,0,0,0"/>
                                    </StackPanel>
                                </Border>
                                
                                <!--触发效果-->
                                <ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                    <!--检查IsCheaked 如果是True，就应用下面的属性-->
                                    <Trigger Property="IsChecked" Value="True">
                                        <Setter TargetName="cheak" Property="Visibility" Value="Visible"/>
                                        <Setter TargetName="text" Property="Margin" Value="20,0,0,0"/>
                                        <Setter TargetName="uncheak" Property="Visibility" Value="Collapsed"/>
                                        <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background">
                                            <Setter.Value>
                                                <!--Background 这里要实现渐变效果 比较复杂-->
                                                <LinearGradientBrush StartPoint="0,0" EndPoint="1,0">
                                                    <GradientStop Color="#8000"/>
                                                    <GradientStop Offset="1" Color="Transparent"/>
                                                </LinearGradientBrush>
                                            </Setter.Value>
                                        </Setter>
                                    </Trigger>
                                    
                                </ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                
                            </ControlTemplate>
                        </Setter.Value>
                    </Setter>
                </Style>
            </StackPanel.Resources>

            <RadioButton Content="蒙德" Command="{Binding LoadCityCommand}" IsChecked="True"/>
            <RadioButton Content="璃月" Command="{Binding LoadCityCommand}"/>
            <RadioButton Content="稻妻" Command="{Binding LoadCityCommand}"/>
            <RadioButton Content="须弥" Command="{Binding LoadCityCommand}"/>
            <RadioButton Content="敬请期待" IsEnabled="False"/>
        </StackPanel>
```
